characterDescription.skinTone: light-medium olive skin with warm yellow undertones, freckles concentrated on nose bridge and cheeks, some redness around nose and mouth
characterDescription.eyeColor: hazel green-brown eyes with darker limbal ring and subtle golden flecks
characterDescription.eyeShape: almond-shaped eyes, slightly downturned at outer corners, moderate upper eyelid exposure
characterDescription.hairColor: dark brown hair with warm auburn undertones, sun-bleached lighter brown streaks throughout, especially around the face
characterDescription.hairTexture: slightly wavy hair with medium thickness
characterDescription.hairStyle: long hair parted slightly off-center to the right, falling loosely around shoulders
characterDescription.faceShape: oval face with a slightly wider forehead and a gentle jawline, defined cheekbones
characterDescription.nose: medium-sized nose with a straight bridge and a rounded tip, nostrils slightly flared
characterDescription.lips: medium-sized lips with a slightly fuller upper lip than the lower, natural rosy pink color
characterDescription.smile: slight, closed-lip smile, no teeth visible
characterDescription.eyebrows: medium-thick dark brown eyebrows, slightly arched shape, well-groomed
characterDescription.ears: partially visible ears close to head
characterDescription.cheeks: slightly full cheeks, more pronounced freckles, natural rosiness
characterDescription.facialProportions: balanced proportions, with eyes, nose and mouth proportionally sized in relation to the oval face shape
characterDescription.distinctiveFeatures: Dense freckles across the nose bridge and cheeks. Slight asymmetry around the mouth - left side of lip appears slightly higher. Very subtle nasolabial folds. Minor dark circles under the eyes.
characterDescription.overallImpression: Warm, natural appearance with a relaxed and friendly expression. Features give a healthy and slightly sun-kissed impression.
characterDescription.fullDescription: The subject is a woman estimated to be between 35 and 40 years old with light-medium olive skin that displays warm yellow undertones and a concentrated pattern of freckles across the nose and cheeks. Her almond-shaped hazel green-brown eyes are slightly downturned at the outer corners and framed by medium-thick dark brown eyebrows with a subtly arched shape. She has dark brown, slightly wavy hair with warm auburn undertones and sun-bleached lighter streaks, worn long and parted slightly off-center. Her face is oval-shaped with defined cheekbones, and a medium-sized nose featuring a straight bridge and rounded tip. She has a gentle, closed-lip smile, with subtle nasolabial folds beginning to show, enhancing her natural warmth.
